https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/YM5JbehCJfDN28fJTHGEcOVVzI.jpg The DVD portion of the Remains CD/DVD package gives fans a peek behind the Alkaline Trio curtain. Having taken a videographer with them on their last few tours, the band has captured hundreds of hours of backstage, behind-thescenes, and live footage. This is the first DVD of its kind by the Trio, so fans are bound to be excited! Package contains a DVD featuring behind-the-scenes, backstage, and live footage.
